data.description: Seller is offering a $1,500 Buyer Broker Bonus with closing by 2/22/24. Gorgeous Quad Level, Brick Home in the heart of Munster is right down the street from Frank Hammond schools! This one boasts 4 finished completely levels, a fenced-in yard w/beautiful in-ground pool, a heated driveway & garage floor, & so much more! Enter the main level foyer to find a spacious Living / Dining Room Combination complete with hardwood floors. The eat-in kitchen is open-concept and has been completely renovated with new granite, cabinetry, floors, and SS appliances. Upstairs you'll find 3 nice-sized bedrooms, the lower level boasts a huge recreation room with a gas fireplace and bath, along with entry to the garage. The lowest level of the home was completely remodeled down to the studs & concrete floor and includes additional finished recreational space and a space to use as an office or guest bedroom.
